# Performance Optimization

**Profile first, optimize second — never guess at bottlenecks.**

## Measure before changing
- Frontend: React DevTools Profiler, Lighthouse, bundle analyzer
- Backend: query logging, heap snapshots, APM traces
- Database: EXPLAIN ANALYZE

## Common bottleneck areas
- Frontend: unnecessary re-renders, large bundle, unoptimized assets
- Backend: N+1 queries, sync I/O in hot paths, connection pool exhaustion
- DB: missing indexes, full table scans, lock contention
- Algorithm: O(n²) loops, redundant computation

## Safe first optimizations
- Caching (memoization, Redis, HTTP headers)
- Lazy loading and code splitting
- Database indexes on query predicates
- Batch operations over one-by-one loops

## Output: current metric → bottleneck with evidence → fix → verification method → trade-offs
